<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>Ride Details</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="css/rideDetails.css">
</head>

<body>
    <div class="container" id="ct"> 
    <h1>Ride Details</h1>
    <p>Name: {{ride.name}}</p>
    <p>From: {{ride.from}}</p>
    <p>To: {{ride.to}}</p>
    <p>Seats: {{ride.seats}}</p>
    <p>Date: {{dateFormat ride.date}}</p>
    <p>Time: {{ride.time}}</p>
    <p>Vehicle: {{ride.vehicletype}}</p>
    <p>Price: â‚¹{{ride.price}}</p>
    <p>Contact: +91 {{ride.contact}} &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;(Please note the phone number and call the driver before you book the ride)</p>
    <h3>Communication with driver</h3>
    <p class="desc">"To ensure that your ride goes smoothly, we recommend our users to call their driver before booking to discuss any
        special requirements or details
        with their driver before making a booking. This will help
        to ensure that both parties are on the same page and can make necessary arrangements. After the call, you can
        proceed with booking the ride with confidence. Thank you for your cooperation and understanding."</p>
    <form id="bookform" action="/bookings/{{ride._id}}" method="POST">
        <input type="hidden" name="rideId" value="{{ride._id}}">
        <button type="submit" id="btnbook">Book ride</button>
    </form>
    </div>
</body>

</html>
